                  </hi>. I live in Dove-row, Hackney—I was at a pub<lb></lb>lic-house near St. John's-street, early in the morning on the 22nd of February—the prisoner came up to me and took the watch out of my pocket—I immediately pursued him, and called out, "Stop thief"—he was taken by a policeman—this is my watch—I am positive he is the man.</p>
