               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defense.</hi> I was coming from the play; I heard three or four cry, "stop thief;" I ran, and the policeman asked me if I had robbed a man of a watch; I said, "What watch?" the gentleman tin came up, he asked if I took the watch from him, and he said he thought so; there was a young man passed that knew me, and he took him as well as me.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
